	quest.2DBB88E1C147F496.quest_desc: [
		"You need &e55 &bCreate Mechanical Crafters&r shaped as a &dstar&r (upside down compared to &6Patrick&r and &6ATM Stars&r) to craft your first &dPika Star&r."
		""
		"Place &5Altar&r on the ground, check recipe of &dPika Star&r, click the center item - &6Imbued Egg&r. On the left bottom corner of the recipe click the block to see the &bpattern&r your crafters should be."
